The boy laughed at the beggar. Change it into passive voice-
option1: The beggar was laughed by the boy.
option2: The beggar was being laughed by the boy.
option3: The beggar was being laughed at by the boy.
option4: The beggar was laughed at by the boy.
explanation: প্রথমে Object (The begger) কে subject হিসেবে + auxiliary verb-was (past indefinite অনুসারে) + V3 (laughed at-group verb) + preposition (by) + subject (the boy) কে object হিসেবে করা হয়েছে।
